  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective randomized clinical trial to determine where is the optimal location
      for local anesthetic injection for ultrasound guided interscalene nerve blocks.  The
      investigators are investigating if local anesthetic deposited between the nerve roots is
      more effective than local anesthetic deposited in the interscalene groove.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
